---
title: inkyvoxel
description: I am a software engineer who writes about various topics including web applications and cybersecurity.
layout: layout.liquid
pagination:
    data: collections.post
    size: 5
    alias: posts
    reverse: true
---
<section>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "Blog",
      "name": "{{ title }}",
      "description": "{{ description }}",
      "url": "{{ site.url }}",
      "author": {
        "@type": "Person",
        "name": "Mark Brady"
      }
    }
  </script>
  <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
  <p>
    Hello, and welcome to my website! My name is Mark. I write about various <a href="/tags">topics</a>, including
    software engineering and cybersecurity.
  </p>
  <p>You can subscribe to future posts using the <a href="/feed.atom">feed</a>.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Latest posts</h2>

  {% for post in posts %}
    <article>
      <h3>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      </h3>
      <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      <p class="date">
        <time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
      </p>
      <hr>
    </article>
  {% endfor %}

  <nav>
    {% if pagination.href.previous %}
      <a href="{{ pagination.href.previous }}">Newer posts</a>
    {% endif %}

    {% if pagination.href.previous and pagination.href.next %}
      |
    {% endif %}

    {% if pagination.href.next %}
      <a href="{{ pagination.href.next }}">Older posts</a>
    {% endif %}
  </nav>
</section>
